check out Jerome Kersey, who fell headfirst over the back of a teammate. Kersey 
left under his own power but did not return to the game. ; Photo, Laker guard 
Magic Johnson looks for an open passing lane as Clyde Drexler of the Trail 
Blazers defends Tuesday night at the Forum. MICHAEL EDWARDS / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
