<P>
LOS ANGELES COUNTY -- ELECTIONS; PROPOSITIONS; PROPOSITION A (JAIL BOND; 
PROPOSITION B (PARK BOND); PROPOSITION C (TRANSIT BOND); PROPOSITION J (911 
SYSTEM); PROPOSITION K (HOUSING BOND) 
</P>
