UNITED STATES -- ELECTIONS; UNITED STATES -- PUBLIC WORKS; TRENDS; UNITED 
STATES -- PUBLIC FACILITIES; TELECOMMUNICATIONS; TECHNOLOGY; GOVERNMENT 
REGULATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
