<SUBJECT>
<P>
CONSULTANTS; FEES; TAGGART, LAWRENCE W; LINCOLN SAVINGS &amp; LOANS 
ASSOCIATION; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; CONFLICT OF INTEREST 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA110790-0100 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 304311 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 7, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
