<HEADLINE>
<P>
PHYSICIAN'S TRIBUTE TO AN UNCOMMON BRAVERY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
On behalf of the UCI Clinical Cancer Center faculty and staff, I would like to 
express our sincere appreciation for your tribute to Maria Flores. 
</P>
<P>
Medical professionals and care givers face the difficult burden of losing 
terminally ill patients continually; yet when confronted by the loss of a 
courageous patient -- particularly a young child -- the strain is all the more 
profound. 
</P>
<P>
Your acknowledgement of Maria's uncommon bravery and attitude was a great 
comfort to her family, friends, and care givers. Indeed, they will treasure 
both the June article and September memorial tribute. 
</P>
<P>
Thank you again for your sensitivity and understanding. 
</P>
<P>
FRANK K. MEYSKENS JR., MD, FACP, 
</P>
<P>
Irvine 
</P>
</TEXT>
